Paper: hep-th/9302123

Date: 1993-02-25

Title: Adler-Bardeen theorem and vanishing of the gauge beta function

Authors: O. Piguet and S.P. Sorella

Comments: 11p., UGVA-DPT 1992/07-774, to be publ. in Nucl. Phys. B

Journal-ref: Nucl.Phys. B395 (1993) 661-671

The proof of the non-renormalization theorem for the gauge anomaly offour-dimensional theories is extended to the case of models with a vanishingone-loop gauge beta function.